metadata.name: Guess?
metadata.description: It is a collection of 10,000 nfts created algorithmically, inspired by comics. Special nfts consisting of +400 unique features have been selected from among 1 million possibilities. This collection, which is the beginning of major projects, believes in nature, animals and bitcoin technology, and plans to create a clean technology for our future by protecting natural life. 80% of all secondary sales will go towards in-game rewards and a community wallet for War-affected children and animals. We will develop a passive income game by issuing cryptocurrencies with the aim of increasing the NFT price and value.
